#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.194"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.194:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.194:0.2"
msgid "20. Mahāvagga"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: sāpugiyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.194:0.3"
msgid "194. Sāmugiyasutta"
msgstr ""

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: sāmugaṃ nāma → sāpūgaṃ nāma (bj) | sāpugaṃ nāma (s1-3, km) | sāpūgannāma (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.194:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ānando koliyesu viharati sāmugaṃ nāma koliyānaṃ nigamo."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: sāmugiyā → sāpugiyā (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an4.194:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā sāmugiyā koliyaputtā yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; "
"upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ "
"nisinne kho te sāmugiye koliyaputte āyasmā ānando etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.195"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: sokaparidevānaṃ → sokapariddavānaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.194:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Cattārimāni, byagghapajjā, pārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgāni tena bhagavatā jānatā "
"passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena sammadakkhātāni sattānaṃ visuddhiyā "
"sokaparidevānaṃ samatikkamāya dukkhadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamāya ñāyassa "
"adhigamāya nibbānassa sacchikiriyāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:2.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:2.3"
msgid ""
"Sīlapārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ, cittapārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ, "
"diṭṭhipārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ, vimuttipārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.194:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, byagghapajjā, sīlapārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, byagghapajjā, bhikkhu sīlavā hoti … pe … samādāya sikkhati "
"sikkhāpadesu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:3.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, byagghapajjā, sīlapārisuddhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:3.4"
msgid ""
"Iti evarūpiṃ sīlapārisuddhiṃ aparipūraṃ vā paripūressāmi paripūraṃ vā tattha "
"tattha paññāya anuggahessāmīti, yo tattha chando ca vāyāmo ca ussāho ca "
"ussoḷhī ca appaṭivānī ca sati ca sampajaññañca, idaṃ vuccati, byagghapajjā, "
"sīlapārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.194:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, byagghapajjā, cittapārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, byagghapajjā, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … catutthaṃ jhānaṃ "
"upasampajja viharati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, byagghapajjā, cittapārisuddhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:4.4"
msgid ""
"Iti evarūpiṃ cittapārisuddhiṃ aparipūraṃ vā paripūressāmi paripūraṃ vā "
"tattha tattha paññāya anuggahessāmīti, yo tattha chando ca vāyāmo ca ussāho "
"ca ussoḷhī ca appaṭivānī ca sati ca sampajaññañca, idaṃ vuccati, "
"byagghapajjā, cittapārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.194:5.1"
msgid "Katamañca, byagghapajjā, diṭṭhipārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, byagghapajjā, bhikkhu ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘"
"ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:5.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, byagghapajjā, diṭṭhipārisuddhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:5.4"
msgid ""
"Iti evarūpiṃ diṭṭhipārisuddhiṃ aparipūraṃ vā … pe … tattha tattha paññāya "
"anuggahessāmīti, yo tattha chando ca vāyāmo ca ussāho ca ussoḷhī ca "
"appaṭivānī ca sati ca sampajaññañca, idaṃ vuccati, byagghapajjā, "
"diṭṭhipārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.196"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.194:6.1"
msgid "Katamañca, byagghapajjā, vimuttipārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:6.2"
msgid ""
"Sa kho so, byagghapajjā, ariyasāvako iminā ca sīlapārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgena "
"samannāgato iminā ca cittapārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgena samannāgato iminā ca "
"diṭṭhipārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgena samannāgato rajanīyesu dhammesu cittaṃ "
"virājeti, vimocanīyesu dhammesu cittaṃ vimoceti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:6.3"
msgid ""
"So rajanīyesu dhammesu cittaṃ virājetvā, vimocanīyesu dhammesu cittaṃ "
"vimocetvā sammāvimuttiṃ phusati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:6.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, byagghapajjā, vimuttipārisuddhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.194:6.5"
msgid ""
"Iti evarūpiṃ vimuttipārisuddhiṃ aparipūraṃ vā paripūressāmi paripūraṃ vā "
"tattha tattha paññāya anuggahessāmīti, yo tattha chando ca vāyāmo ca ussāho "
"ca ussoḷhī ca appaṭivānī ca sati ca sampajaññañca, idaṃ vuccati, "
"byagghapajjā, vimuttipārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.194:7.1"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, byagghapajjā, cattāri pārisuddhipadhāniyaṅgāni tena bhagavatā "
"jānatā passatā arahatā sammāsambuddhena sammadakkhātāni sattānaṃ visuddhiyā "
"sokaparidevānaṃ samatikkamāya dukkhadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamāya ñāyassa "
"adhigamāya nibbānassa sacchikiriyāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.194:7.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
